{"tid":1787893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[劏開車頂]新田公路九巴撞樹逾40人浴血3人拋出車","createTime":"2019-12-18T09:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T11:31:04.000Z","uid":203799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ee09087298553e996de3e34a1fade94b778ecb7c","tid":1787893,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"新田公路近古洞一帶發生嚴重交通意外。下午4時左右，一輛九巴在上述位置懷疑失控撞樹，整個巴士車頂被削去，情況嚴重，大批消防員和救護員在現場搶救。據悉現場傷者超過40人，更有3人被抛出車外，情況未明。<br />\n讀者黃先生經過現場，表示現場有多人受傷，部份人更失去知覺，警方封鎖兩條行車線進行救援，現場交通擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ovO4oR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ovO4oR.png&h=b4bd0c68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pxwyv3T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxwyv3T.png&h=07e5284b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0rR2aA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0rR2aA.png&h=4296f55f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191218&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60391945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191218%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60391945&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Buq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=c93991c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191218%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60391945&h=058dc0c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191218&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60391945</a>"},{"pid":"479a527a779e5dcd64f85dc3c0a6f90b951a1639","tid":1787893,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b6bd78d7a60a3280e996945c0db47a1207fd58","tid":1787893,"uid